# Week 0 — CS50 Python

## Indoor Voice

Goal:
Convert text to lowercase.

Concept learned:
.lower()

Example similar code learned:

```python
city = input("City: ")
print(city.lower())
```

Lesson:
Strings have methods that modify text.

